### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082/api/v1
@userId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
@postId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001

### Create Post
# @name createPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
    "title": "Sample Post Title",
    "content": "This is a sample post content with more details.",
    "visibility": "PUBLIC",
    "hashtags": ["tech", "programming"],
    "mediaUrls": [
        "https://example.com/image1.jpg",
        "https://example.com/image2.jpg"
    ]
}

### Get Post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Get User Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?page=0&size=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Get Feed
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/feed?page=0&size=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Update Post
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
    "title": "Updated Post Title",
    "content": "This is the updated content of the post.",
    "visibility": "FOLLOWERS_ONLY",
    "hashtags": ["updated", "tech"],
    "mediaUrls": [
        "https://example.com/updated-image.jpg"
    ]
}

### Delete Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/metrics

### OpenAPI Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/swagger-ui/index.html